title: The Cuinn Psalter 1965
description: Coslett Quinn (1907-1995) was a minister in the Church of Ireland, and after taking the post of Professor of Biblical Greek at Trinity College, Dublin. In 1961, he translated the Psalter for Leabhar na hUrna√≠ Coitinne (The Book of Common Prayer) of the Church of Ireland in 1965. This translation follows the version of the Great Bible of 1539.
